trip.name: Peak To Peak
trip.description: The Peak to Peak is a brutal hill workout going through Lake Oswego, eventually climbing up the second peak, Mountain Park, to give you a 360 degree view of surrounding suburbia and Portland to the north.  Some very steep hills!

user.description: I work on this site with Zack Ham, I love my job!
